719506f-a.text:
East Houston Street, (entire left and the foreground of the right) west from (No. 270) but not including Ave. B. The triangular structure (No. 2-4 Ave A ) divides this street from East 1st Street, which the portion on the rigght becomes, when west of Ave. A. Note the 1st Street Station
of the Second Ave. Elevated Line, on First Ave.
March 13, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.

719505f-a.text:
East Houston Street, north side, west from (No. 270), but not including Ave. B. This side of East Houston Street, becomes East 1st Strcet, when west of Ave. A. Note the Station of the Second and Third Aves., Elevated
on First Ave.
April 3, 1935.
L Sperr.
